                <li><strong>Free</strong>: 2k DUs, 500 Runs, 1 Connector, community support</li>
                <li><strong>Pro ($999)</strong>: 5M DUs, 100k Runs, 10 Connectors, 5k MAUs, SLA & chat</li>
                <li><strong>Business ($4,999)</strong>: 25M DUs, 500k Runs, 25 Connectors, 25k MAUs, SSO/SCIM, 99.9% SLA</li>
                <li><strong>Enterprise (Custom)</strong>: Dedicated tenancy/VPC, FIPS mode, 24/7 support</li>
